Class AHOrgModelImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.liferay.portal.model.impl.BaseModelImpl<AHOrg>
      • de.fraunhofer.fokus.oefit.adhoc.model.impl.AHOrgModelImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.liferay.portal.model.BaseModel<AHOrg>, com.liferay.portal.model.ClassedModel, AHOrgModel, Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<AHOrg>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AHOrgBaseImpl

    public class AHOrgModelImpl
extends com.liferay.portal.model.impl.BaseModelImpl<AHOrg>
implements AHOrgModel
    The base model implementation for the AHOrg service. Represents a row in the "AHORG" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    This implementation and its corresponding interface AHOrgModel exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in AHOrgImpl.

    Author:
    Brian Wing Shun Chan
    See Also:
    AHOrgImpl, AHOrg, AHOrgModel, Serialized Form
